      "id": "PopularPost25756",
      "post_content": "I played a Zendikar tournament today. I had 2 life left and my opponent had 13. I played [Day of Judgment](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Day of Judgment) (Wrath of God except creatures can regenerate) Which killed my opponents 6 green token, 2 white flying token, 3 creatures, and my two flying 2/2s  \n  \nI played this card, [Terra Stomper](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=186321), put a [Trusty Machete](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Trusty Machete) on him for a nice 10/9 creatures. Game Over. The game was pretty epic ended up drawing 1-1 with the guy.",
